#: ../../docs/classes/class_backbuffercopy.rst:43
msgid ""
"**COPY_MODE_DISABLED** = **0** --- Disables the buffering mode. This "
"means the BackBufferCopy node will directly use the portion of screen it "
"covers."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_backbuffercopy.rst:45
msgid ""
"**COPY_MODE_RECT** = **1** --- BackBufferCopy buffers a rectangular "
"region."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_backbuffercopy.rst:47
msgid ""
"**COPY_MODE_VIEWPORT** = **2** --- BackBufferCopy buffers the entire "
"screen."
msgstr ""

